Activity 1: Creating a tab for Course Object

Go to the setup page → type Tabs in Quick Find bar
Click on tabs
Click on New (under custom object tab).
Select Object (Course) >> Select the tab style
Click on Next >> (Add to profiles page) keep it as default >> Click on Next (Add to Custom App) uncheck the include tab.
Make sure that the Append tab to the user's existing personal customizations is checked.
Click save

